ADD
  Create or reconfigure a nation slot.  (Deity only.)

SYNTAX
  add <cnum|?> <name> <representative> <status>

DESCRIPTION
  Creates a new nation or resets an existing slot.  Only the deity
  (country 0) can use this command.

  <cnum>          - country number (1-99), or '?' to auto-assign
  <name>          - country name (max 20 characters)
  <representative>- player's representative name (max 20 chars)
  <status>        - one of:
                     v  visitor    (read-only access)
                     p  player     (full play access)
                     g  god        (deity status)
                     d  delete     (mark slot unused)

  New nations start with no territory.  Use the world generator or
  manual sector assignment to give them starting land.

EXAMPLE
  add ? Mordor Sauron p      create next free country as player
  add 5 Gondor Aragorn p     set country 5 to active player
  add 3 Ghost ghost d        delete/reset country 3

SEE ALSO
  nation  enable  shutdown  change
